org.perfcake.message.correlator

Class PrefixCorrelator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.correlator.AbstractCorrelator
      • org.perfcake.message.correlator.PrefixCorrelator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Correlator

    public class PrefixCorrelator
extends AbstractCorrelator
    Extract a prefix from the message and then the same prefix is expected to be in the response. It should be used where messages cannot have headers for instance.
